ey Sees &lsquo;Ominous&rsquo; Signs of Another Asian Debt Crisis</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-20/omens-of-another-asian-debt-crisis-seen-by-mckinsey-in-stresses\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-20%2Fomens-of-another-asian-debt-crisis-seen-by-mckinsey-in-stresses&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46%2F1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=0b21ecae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-20/omens-of-another-asian-debt-crisis-seen-by-mckinsey-in-stresses</a>"}]}